msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cjwt-claims.md:68
msgid ""
"After successful JWT validation in `jwt.middleware.ts`, the decoded payload "
"is attached to `req.user`:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cjwt-claims.md:70
msgid ""
"interface JwtClaims {\n"
"  sub: string; // → userId in audit log\n"
"  municipality: string; // → tenant isolation filter\n"
"  organisation_type: string; // → propagated to BPMN process variables\n"
"  roles: string[]; // → authorization checks\n"
"  loa: string; // → LoA-gated endpoint checks\n"
"  preferred_username: string;\n"
"  mandate?: string;\n"
"  bsn?: string;\n"
"  employeeId?: string; // → HR onboarding profile lookup\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Creferences%5Cjwt-claims.md:84
msgid ""
"The tenant middleware reads `req.user.municipality` to load the "
"`TenantConfig` and apply the feature allowlist for the request."
msgstr ""

